      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I've been thinking about the tension between religious rights and secular laws. Like, should religious groups be allowed to opt-out of government mandates if those mandates clash with their faith, or does that kind of thing just undermine the secular nature of the state? What's the right way to look at this?",
